Science said prove it, so here we are. 
@katiebeauty put her glam on the line to show how #MACFixPlus seamlessly melds, instantly hydrates and keeps makeup looking fresh for 12 hours.
I'll take three Fix+ Mattes...two Stay Overs and one of those M·A·C crewnecks, please. #MACFixPlus #MACFixPlusHacks

Some people collect shoes, we collect #MACFixPlus — and every single one deserves its spot. 

💧Fix+: The makeup-melding mist for before and between each layer of your routine.
💧Fix+ Magic Radiance: The mist-on moisturizer that helps plump and rehydrate skin with a dewy finish.
💧Fix+ Stay Over: The makeup-locking mist that sets your look for 24 whole hours. 
💧Fix+ Matte: The mattifying mist that controls the look of oil and reduces the appearance of pores.

@macprooslo

#MACFixPlus stays booked and busy. Always ready to refresh your look, meld your makeup and improve the quality of makeup wear for up to 12 hours.
